Package: RJSMC
Title: Sequential Monte Carlo with Reversible-Jump for inference about multiple changepoint model
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Emanuele",
           family = "Gramuglia",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "emanuele.gramuglia@kantega.no",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package performis on-line inference for learning changepoints and state values 
             of Marked non-Honogenous Poisson Process. The Algorithm used for approximating the target
             distribution is the Squential Monte Carlo. Furthermore, due to that the importnat density
              cannot be directly used for proposing new values, Reversible Jump MCMC iterations
             are perfomed from obtaining samples from it.
